event.title: Best Engineering college in Delhi
event.description:
Best Engineering college in Delhi
J.C. Bose University of Science and Technology, YMCA, Faridabad.
NGF College of Engineering & Technology (NGFCET) is being run under the aegis of New Green Field Educational Society, Delhi. The society is in the field of education since 1964. The college is approved by AICTE, DTE, Govt of Haryana. The college is spread over 26 acres of land and located at a 71Km stone on NH-2, Palwal, Faridabad.
